    .area-white.delta
      .inner-row
        h2 Why uPort?
        .explainer-section
          img.exp-graphic(src='img/simple-to-integrate.svg')
          .exp-text
            h3 Give users control over their identity and data.
            p Uport is Ethereum's identity platform. Self-sovereign, user centric keys and data management using Ethereum smart contracts. Support decentralized identity and user data. Self-sovereign identity platform built using Ethereum. User-centric data and reputation protocol.
